These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Sport: cycling, surfing, rowing, swimming
Hobby: board-games, gardening, hiking, sudoku
1. Sport:surfing is between Sport:cycling and Hobby:gardening##2
2. Sport:surfing is on the left or right of Hobby:board-games##3
3. Sport:surfing is somewhere between Sport:swimming and Sport:cycling##7
4. Hobby:gardening is in an even position##4
5. Sport:swimming is on the right of Hobby:hiking##1
6. Hobby:gardening is somewhere to the left of Hobby:board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Sport   | rowing | swimming       | surfing | cycling        |
| Hobby      | hiking  | gardening | sudoku        | board-games |

