.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Pet: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
Beverage: sprite, almond-milk, coffee, hot-chocolate
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:coffee and Pet:hedgehog##7
2. Pet:snake is somewhere to the left of Pet:dog##5
3. Pet:snake is somewhere to the right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##5
4. Pet:goat is on the left of Pet:snake##1
5. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:coffee and Beverage:almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk   | hot-chocolate | coffee | sprite |

