.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Music-Genre: funk, disco, dubstep, d&b
Sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. Music-Genre:funk is somewhere between Sport:golf and Music-Genre:d&b##7
3. Music-Genre:dubstep == Sport:volleyball##1
4. Sport:skateboarding is on the left of Sport:volleyball##1
5. Music-Genre:disco is on the left of Sport:climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco | funk | d&b       | dubstep |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

